this # Chatbot for FAQs

This project is a simple FAQ chatbot developed as part of the *CodeAlpha Internship Program*.  
The chatbot answers user questions by matching them with the most relevant FAQ using basic Natural Language Processing techniques.

---

## ðŸš€ Project Overview

The Chatbot for FAQs is designed to:
- Respond to user queries based on predefined Frequently Asked Questions
- Match user input with the closest question
- Display the most relevant answer in a simple chatbot interface

